17 paucissimos sensus et angustas sententias: Of this style, Seneca is our only extant representative. Cf. Quint. X 1, 130 si rerum pondera minutissimis sententiis non fraqi-eset (sc. Seneca). IX 3, 74 f. XII 10, 46 ff. Sen. Ep. 100, 5. 114. On the meaning of ‘ sensus ' and ‘ sententia,' see note c. 20 16.
